(478, 1269, 'Human After All', '⊙散發舞動歡樂氣氛舞曲製造機、再戰復古與新潮樂音結合之冠軍巴黎雙人DJ組、睽違四年第三張全新大碟『Human After All回歸』當中同名Maxi混音單曲\r\n\r\n⊙收錄(Kylie/Giving You Up、Freeform Five/No More Conversations、Tiefschwarz/Wait & See) 日前以Rocker一曲震驚全球樂壇之德國Electro雙人組 Alter Ego + (Annie/Happy Without You) JF Sebastian + (Fatboy Slim/Don’t Let The Man Get You Down) Justice + (Royksopp/What Else Is There?、Psychonauts/World Keeps Turning) Emperor Machine + Disco-Punk運動風潮音樂大廠DFA唱片旗下大將 皇麥克林 The Juan Maclean等知名藝人操刀之全新舞曲混音 \r\n\r\n資料來源：EMI', '2005-03-15 00:00:00', 0, 1, 3, '', '', 0, '', 0, 0, '2008-05-12 22:20:36', '2015-02-16 15:46:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
